Scenario: Change passcode error(operatorid is null/empty)
Given an initial data from {MST_USER_CREDENTIALS_forViewEmployee.xml}
Given a Credential Resource
When I change the oldpasscode{100} of operator{} to newpasscode{111}
Then I should get resultcode {310}
When I change the oldpasscode{100} of operator{null} to newpasscode{111}
Then I should get resultcode {310}

!-- Change passcode error(oldpasscode is incorrect)
When I change the oldpasscode{101} of operator{100} to newpasscode{111}
Then I should get resultcode {306}

!-- Change passcode error(operatorid not found)
When I change the oldpasscode{101} of operator{101} to newpasscode{111}
Then I should get resultcode {305}

!-- Change passcode error(newpasscode length is 31)
When I change the oldpasscode{100} of operator{100} to newpasscode{0123456789012345678901234567890}
Then I should get resultcode {134}

